Jewellery ERP & Girvi Management Platform

Authentication Module Specification v1.0

Module Code: MOD-AUTH
Priority: Critical MVP
Version: 1.0
Frontend: Flutter + BLoC
Backend: NestJS
Dependencies: Firebase Auth, Device Management, RBAC, Audit Module

⸻

1. Module Purpose

Authentication Module is the security gateway for the entire platform.

Responsibilities:

* OTP Authentication
* Device Registration
* Device Approval
* PIN Login
* Biometric Login
* Session Management
* Token Management
* Logout
* Security Enforcement

No module can be accessed before successful authentication.

⸻

2. Business Objectives

BO-001

Prevent unauthorized access.

BO-002

Ensure only approved devices access tenant data.

BO-003

Minimize login time for counter staff.

BO-004

Support offline counter operations.

BO-005

Maintain complete auditability.

